PN,44101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,FPredatory behaviour features in 30% of
OL,7,Fthe most serious cases investigated by
OL,8,Fthe Police Ombudsman for Northern
OL,9,FIreland.
OL,11,FA new report, Abuse of Position for
OL,12,FSexual Purposes (APSP) by PSNI
OL,13,FOfficers: Analysis and Emerging
OL,14,FFindings, analysed allegations
OL,15,Finvolving officers (all male and aged
OL,16,Fbetween 30 and 50) between 2018 to
OL,17,F2024.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,FThe report also highlights
OL,7,Fvulnerabilities of the 36 victims (all
OL,8,Ffemale) identified in the cases, from
OL,9,Fbeing a victim of crime, to mental
OL,10,Fhealth issues, domestic abuse,
OL,11,Fsuicidal ideation or addiction.
OL,13,FSome victims were involved in crimes
OL,14,Fthemselves, which the report found
OL,15,Fmade them more vulnerable to
OL,16,Fexploitation by a police officer.
OL,18,FThe findings include that in three
OL,19,Fcases the officer had sexual contact
OL,20,Fwith the victim on the same day they
OL,21,Fmet in the course of his duties.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,FIn two thirds of cases there was a
OL,7,Fgradual escalation of contact with the
OL,8,Fvictim by the officer over a period,
OL,9,Fvarying from text and social media
OL,10,Fmessages to visits to the victim's
OL,11,Fhouse.
OL,13,FIn a further ten of the
OL,14,Finvestigations, the officer had
OL,15,Fengaged in sexual contact with the
OL,16,Ffemale within a month, and in one case
OL,17,Fcontact is reported to have taken
OL,18,Fplace over the course of 20 years.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,FThere was evidence of targeted
OL,7,Fexploitation of women, with police
OL,8,Fofficers often making inappropriate
OL,9,Fuse of police systems to identify
OL,10,Fwomen for sexual exploitation or
OL,11,Facquire further information in
OL,12,Frelation to potential victims.
OL,14,FPolice Ombudsman chief executive Hugh
OL,15,FHume described some of the findings as
OL,16,Fshocking.
OL,18,FHe also said they hope the publication
OL,19,Fof the report will reassure victims
OL,20,Fthey can come forward and know their
OL,21,Fcomplaint will be taken seriously.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,F"Although this is a small number of
OL,7,Fofficers relative to the size of the
OL,8,FPSNI, the abuse of their position for
OL,9,Ftheir own sexual gain inflicts
OL,10,Fsignificant and long-lasting damage on
OL,11,Ftheir victims," he said.
OL,13,F"Such is the power imbalance that many
OL,14,Fwomen do not report the offending
OL,15,Fdirectly for fear of reprisal, and
OL,16,Fothers can be so vulnerable that they
OL,17,Fdo not recognise that the officer is
OL,18,Fabusing them and instead see him as a
OL,19,F'knight in shining armour' figure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@OO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,F"Others do not see themselves as
OL,7,Fvictims at all.
OL,9,F"We hope one of the outcomes of
OL,10,Fpublishing this report will be that
OL,11,Fany woman who has had a similar
OL,12,Fexperience with a police officer will
OL,13,Ffeel reassured that we take this kind
OL,14,Fof offending seriously and know that
OL,15,Fif this has happened to them, we will
OL,16,Flisten and we will investigate."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,FMr Hume said the Ombudsman's office is
OL,7,Fcurrently investigating allegations of
OL,8,Fpolice predatory behaviour which
OL,9,Finvolve a total of 39 victims and 20
OL,10,Fserving and two former police officers.
OL,12,F"We are seeing a rise in these cases
OL,13,Fand the majority of those are coming
OL,14,Ffrom the PSNI itself," he said.
OL,16,F"This is welcome and shows a very
OL,17,Fclear willingness at the most senior
OL,18,Flevel to identify and eradicate this
OL,19,Fkind of behaviour.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@VO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,F"I hope this analysis will support the
OL,7,FPSNI further in recognising and
OL,8,Faddressing predatory police behaviour,
OL,9,Fas well as strengthening their systems
OL,10,Fso the opportunity for this type of
OL,11,Fcorruption is reduced."
OL,13,FChief Constable Jon Boutcher said any
OL,14,Fabuse of position for sexual purposes
OL,15,Fis "wholly unacceptable".
OL,17,F"It represents a serious breach of
OL,18,Ftrust and a violation of the standards
OL,19,Frightly expected of police officers,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@WO]wD@DOUwD@XO]yD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,F"The Criminal Justice Inspection
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland in its March 2025
OL,8,Freport found that the Police
OL,9,FOmbudsman's handling of abuse-of-
OL,10,Fposition complaints needed to improve
OL,11,Fand, as this most recent report
OL,12,Frecognises, by focusing on this issue
OL,13,Ftogether we have seen the number of
OL,14,Freferrals and investigations increase.
OL,16,F"I welcomed that report and the clear
OL,17,Fneed for both the PSNI and the
OL,18,FOmbudsman to robustly deal with
OL,19,Fallegations of abuse of power.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,F"While the report identifies serious
OL,7,Findividual misconduct, it also
OL,8,Frecognises the significant work we
OL,9,Fhave done to strengthen professional
OL,10,Fstandards, enhance vetting and
OL,11,Fmisconduct reporting processes and
OL,12,Fensure learning from past failures."
OL,14,FHe described work such as a previous
OL,15,Freview of historical investigations
OL,16,Fafter the murder of Sarah Everard, an
OL,17,Findependent review of performance and
OL,18,Finternal behaviour by Rachel Langdale
OL,19,FKC, and making sexism, misogyny and
OL,20,Fwider unacceptable behaviours a focus
OL,21,Fin a recent workforce inclusion survey.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,F"We will work ever harder with the
OL,7,FPolice Ombudsman and other key
OL,8,Fexternal stakeholders, including
OL,9,Fthrough the independent Langdale
OL,10,FReview, to ensure robust prevention,
OL,11,Fearly identification and decisive
OL,12,Faction against predatory behaviour.
OL,14,F"There is no place for those who
OL,15,Fdisplay such behaviour in the PSNI,"
OL,16,Fhe said.
OL,18,F"The vast majority of our officers and
OL,19,Fstaff serve with integrity and
OL,20,Fdedication. Where standards fall
OL,21,Fshort, we will act decisively.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUwD@dO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,F"Our focus is on protecting the
OL,7,Fvulnerable, maintaining public
OL,8,Fconfidence and ensuring transparency
OL,9,Fand accountability in all that we do."
OL,11,FPolicing Board chairman Mukesh Sharma
OL,12,Fdescribed the report findings as
OL,13,F"deeply concerning", and said it will
OL,14,Fbe a focus of discussion at a board
OL,15,Fmeeting this week.
OL,17,F"The Chief Constable has made it clear
OL,18,Fto the organisation that there will be
OL,19,Fzero tolerance of police officers or
OL,20,Fpolice staff who abuse their position
OL,21,For powers," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@fO]uD@AOUuD@SO]yD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772571963
OL,3,CGirl aged 14 among victims of
OL,4,Cpredatory behaviour by police officers
OL,6,F"The board is currently finalising a
OL,7,Frevised code of ethics for the PSNI
OL,8,Fwhich makes it explicitly clear that
OL,9,Fpolice officers shall not establish or
OL,10,Fcontinue a sexual or improper
OL,11,Frelationship with any victim, witness,
OL,12,Fsuspect, detained person or defendant
OL,13,Farising from their duties.
OL,15,F"Abuse of power is deeply damaging to
OL,16,Fpublic confidence in policing and as a
OL,17,Fboard, we encourage anyone who has
OL,18,Fbeen subject to abuse of power by a
OL,19,Fserving or former officer to contact
OL,20,Fthe office of the Police Ombudsman and
OL,21,Fmake a report."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU}D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
